Licensed under the BSD 3-Clause License (see usrsctp/LICENSE.md).

A portable userland implementation of the SCTP protocol. Bundled as a
submodule from a fork (vikramdattu/usrsctp) carrying ESP-specific patches:
- SPIRAM thread stack allocation
- ESP_PLATFORM thread-safe netif API support
- sin6 overflow fix
- LWIP support layer

The fork's ESP-specific commits are also under the BSD 3-Clause License,
matching upstream.

